</ul>
<p><strong>25 October 2020 - selected by <em>OCuin</em></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Featured page: <a href="/scp-5788">SCP-5788</a> (Partners in sync) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/riemann" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1787775); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1787775&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610167016" alt="Riemann" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1787775)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/riemann" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1787775); return false;">Riemann</a></span></li>
